-- Plan to Boost Biomedical Industry May Be Issue This Year , Securities Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-27T23:09:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-27/plan-to-boost-biomedical-industry-may-be-issue-this-year-securities-says.html
China’s government may announce a
five-year plan for the development of the nation’s biomedical
industry by the end of the year, the China Securities Journal
reported today, citing unidentified government agencies.  Total biomedical industry output may rise to more than 3
trillion yuan by 2015 from about 1 trillion yuan in 2009,
according to the newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  